---
source: tests/parser.rs
expression: "tree(r\"$$a + b$$\")"
---
ROOT@0..9
  PARAGRAPH@0..9
    DISPLAY_MATH@0..9
      DOLLAR@0..1 "$"
      DOLLAR@1..2 "$"
      MATH@2..7
        WORD@2..3 "a"
        WHITESPACE@3..4 " "
        WORD@4..5 "+"
        WHITESPACE@5..6 " "
        WORD@6..7 "b"
      DOLLAR@7..8 "$"
      DOLLAR@8..9 "$"
